data.description: Welcome to Carolina Bay, where you will find this beautiful home nestled on a large 1-acre lot. The front porch was made for rocking chairs and relaxing. As you enter, you will be swept away by the wood look tile flooring, wainscoting, smooth ceilings, and spacious open floor plan. The home also features network wiring. FROG can be used as 5th bedroom, office, game room, or craft room. Both FROG and living room have surround set up with recessed ceiling speakers and floor sub. The dazzling eat-in kitchen boasts both recessed and pendant lighting, stainless steel appliances, a gorgeous tile backsplash, granite countertops, a large island with a breakfast bar, a breakfast/casual dining area, and a walk-in storage pantry. The large family room, with oversized ceiling fan, and gas fireplace is the perfect space for cozy nights in or for entertaining family and friends for a game night. The master bedroom captivates you with the high ceiling, oversized ceiling fan, large walk-in closet, and in-suite bathroom that includes a glass enclosed tile shower. Step outside to discover an outdoor entertainment area, where you can host memorable gatherings with friends and family. Fire up the grill, relax in the saltwater pool, and soak up the joys of outdoor living in your own private oasis thanks to the 6-foot privacy fence with a 4ft live fence along the back that encloses the entire backyard. This home is just a short drive to Summerville, where you will find local dining and shopping options! Don't wait! Come see this home today!
